te host stars, the shape of the observed exoplanet radius distribution\nwill be incorrectly inferred, for both Kepler- and TESS-detected systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Apr 2018 16:56:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 Oct 2018 15:39:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-12"}
