a potential variation size noticeably larger\nthan estimated in our previous work in W7-X \\cite{Regana_nf_57_056004_2017} for\nother plasma parameters and another configuration.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Apr 2018 10:13:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-26"}
